@HHAhmedBinSaeed Akhi, Assalamu alaikum.
I would like to come to the Middle East to help in areas where Muslims need assistance, like Yemen. To grow food and get the impoverished on a self sustainable course. As the CEO of Emirates Group, you could definitely help. JazaakAllah khair. Ali Nuruddin
